{"article_publication_date": "10-16-2005", "fulltext": "\n\t\t\t", "proc_id": "1094855", "abstract": "Structured Design has been described as a \"traditional approach\" and an \"alternative technology\" by the SEI's (Software Engineering Institute) software technology roadmap on their website [July 2005]. While website visitors are cautioned that structured design does not lend itself to object orientation the method has clearly influenced the evolution of object-oriented design practices. This panel brings together software design visionaries to discuss and debate \"echoes\" in software design \"practice\".", "authors": [{"name": "Steven Fraser", "author_profile_id": "81339499863", "affiliation": "QUALCOMM", "person_id": "PP39039573", "email_address": "", "orcid_id": ""}, {"name": "Kent Beck", "author_profile_id": "81100558273", "affiliation": "Three Rivers Institute", "person_id": "PP31047638", "email_address": "", "orcid_id": ""}, {"name": "Grady Booch", "author_profile_id": "81100557878", "affiliation": "IBM", "person_id": "PP31047618", "email_address": "", "orcid_id": ""}, {"name": "Larry Constantine", "author_profile_id": "81100375146", "affiliation": "Constantine & Lockwood", "person_id": "PP14132845", "email_address": "", "orcid_id": ""}, {"name": "Brian Henderson-Sellers", "author_profile_id": "81100023488", "affiliation": "UTS", "person_id": "PP14021169", "email_address": "", "orcid_id": ""}, {"name": "Steve McConnell", "author_profile_id": "81100627170", "affiliation": "Construx", "person_id": "PP14215885", "email_address": "", "orcid_id": ""}, {"name": "Rebecca Wirfs-Brock", "author_profile_id": "81100400353", "affiliation": "Wirfs-Brock Associates", "person_id": "PP17001255", "email_address": "", "orcid_id": ""}, {"name": "Ed Yourdon", "author_profile_id": "81405596230", "affiliation": "NODRUOY", "person_id": "PP14210214", "email_address": "", "orcid_id": ""}], "doi_number": "10.1145/1094855.1094980", "year": "2005", "article_id": "1094980", "conference